{"type": "article", "id": 5204, "title": "办公家具 Workinmotion", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-14T07:39:16Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 21, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233502OpT7t6u8SkiaUxsj.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是俄罗斯设计师 Fedor Katcuba 为联合办公空间设计的一套办公家具 Workinmotion ，由可弯曲的胶合板和丙烯酸制作而成的结构框架简洁且实用。设计师希望通过这套家具的设计，能够尽量减少桌椅从静止到移动状态所需要移动的桌椅数量，也希望能为提升其移动的便利性，给桌角与椅角均配备了脚轮。隐藏在桌面下方的秘密隔间，内置了电源插座，还可以用来存储办公用品。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233459X1hk3mgPlCDbNuMp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233501MG4rjbYwxsuJHk80.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233501ahfjOl1FkuIR3Vzx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233502sfDOC5ZrRjdPKhoL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.4296875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}